body:
I am passing hyperlink value for one of the entries in excel sheet.

> http://localhost:4200/ui/#/case/2007720723

But when i try to access the link its showing till 

>  http://localhost:4200/ui/

 and rest of the part is removed.
Code as below

```
const workbook = new Excel.Workbook();
let sheet = workbook.getWorksheet(1);
 const listHyperlink = this.rowData.map((key, index) => {
      const val = index + 2;
      return 'A' + val;
    });
 listHyperlink.forEach((key: any) => {
      const cellText = sheet.getCell(key).value;
      const navLink  = `${window.location.origin}/ui/#/case/${cellText}`;
      sheet.getCell(key).value = {
        text: sheet.getCell(key).value,
        hyperlink: navLink
      };
    });
```
